SELECT
  id,
  argMax(name, time) AS name,
  SUM(count) AS total_count,
  groupArrayInsertAt(
    0,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(count, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS change_requests_declined
FROM
(
  SELECT
    toStartOfYear(created_at) AS time,
    org_id AS id, argMax(org_login, time) AS name,
    COUNT() AS count
  FROM gh_events
  WHERE type = 'PullRequestEvent' AND action = 'closed' AND pull_merged = 0 AND (org_id IN [1342004]) AND  created_at >= toDate('2015-1-1') AND created_at < dateAdd(month, 1, toDate('2016-12-1'))
  GROUP BY id, time
  
)
GROUP BY id
ORDER BY change_requests_declined[-1] DESC
    LIMIT 3
